    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      TALL
      Indicates row oriented parallelization where a thread is spawned for one or more graph row roots.
      WIDE
      Indicates graph oriented parallelization where threads are spawned as the graph is explored and assembled.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • WIDE

        public static final ParallelFetchDisposition WIDE
        Indicates graph oriented parallelization where threads are spawned as the graph is explored and assembled. Applicable when fetching a small number of graphs but the graph size depth/breadth is large or huge.

      • TALL

        public static final ParallelFetchDisposition TALL
        Indicates row oriented parallelization where a thread is spawned for one or more graph row roots. More applicable when fetching a large number of graph roots and the graph size depth/breadth is small.
